{"parentUuid":"9f93ad77-2984-4b9d-a4ad-8e3f9d6ed5b8","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Mi2vKc9bXtEQL3aJi4T7Fq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Go に**enum はありません**。代わりに `const` + `iota` で似たものを実現します：\n\n```go\n// iota を使った enum 風定数\ntype HttpMethod string\n\nconst (\n    GET    HttpMethod = \"GET\"\n    POST   HttpMethod = \"POST\"\n    PUT    HttpMethod = \"PUT\"\n    DELETE HttpMethod = \"DELETE\"\n)\n```\n\n```go\n// iota で整数型\ntype Status int\n\nconst (\n    StatusPending Status = iota // 0\n    StatusActive                // 1\n    StatusInactive              // 2\n)\n```\n\n型を定義しておくと型安全にはなりますが、値の範囲チェック（他の言語の enum のような網羅チェック）はコンパイラがしてくれないのが弱点です。\n\n`switch` で網羅チェックしたい場合は [exhaustive](https://github.com/nishanths/exhaustive) などの linter を使うのが一般的です。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3740,"cache_read_input_tokens":13682,"output_tokens":320,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3740,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZXyVB7BCuQWrwu5ykdQh","type":"assistant","uuid":"9bf24415-a91a-49e7-afa4-a24d13b7448f","timestamp":"2026-03-29T20:07:21.388Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"15d3662e-5aa5-4d76-97db-b1a070911c01","version":"2.1.84","gitBranch":"enrollment"}
